# Agent context — bank-agent-llm
# Read CLAUDE.md before touching any code. It is the authoritative reference.

## What this project is
Local-first Python CLI + library. Fetches bank statement PDFs from Gmail (OAuth2)
and Outlook (IMAP), parses them, stores transactions in SQLite, categorizes with a
keyword rules engine (99%+ coverage) + Ollama fallback, and renders dashboards via
Rich (terminal) and Streamlit (web).

## Milestone status
M1-M7 done. M8 Chat is next (`bank-agent chat`, Text-to-SQL via Ollama mistral:7b).

## Critical rules
- All DB access through repository layer (`src/bank_agent_llm/storage/repository.py`).
  Never raw SQL outside that module.
- No business logic in `cli.py` — belongs in `pipeline.py` or a domain module.
- Schema changes via Alembic only: `bank-agent db migrate`.
- New bank = new parser file. Never modify an existing parser to add another bank.
- Ollama calls only inside `src/enrichment/` and `src/chat/` (M8).
- Chat interface (M8) must use a read-only SQLAlchemy connection. Never allow writes.
- Do not commit config/config.yaml, .env, config/gmail_credentials.json, config/gmail_token.json.

## Key data facts (as of 2026-04-05)
- 942 transactions, Jul 2025 – Mar 2026, all credit card statements (not savings).
- direction=credit means card payment (abono), NOT income. Tag: pago-tarjeta.
- "Ampliacion de Plazo" parser fix: stores cuota mensual (N/M), not total balance.
  Each installment has description "AMPLIACION DE PLAZO N/M" for unique dedup hash.
- 938/942 tagged. 4 pending (Ollama JSON edge cases). Run `bank-agent enrich`.
- mistral:7b pulled at localhost:11434 and working.

## Daily commands
```
bank-agent fetch          # download new PDFs from Gmail / Outlook
bank-agent import data/raw
bank-agent enrich
bank-agent status         # Rich terminal dashboard
bank-agent dashboard      # Streamlit web dashboard (http://localhost:8501)
```

## Branch conventions
feature/<name> | fix/<name> | docs/<name> | chore/<name>
Commit format: "type: short description" (feat / fix / docs / chore / refactor)
Integration branch: develop. Stable: main.

